## FileContainer.has() method

Return boolean `true` if key is a match.

Signature:

```typescript
has(key: string): boolean;
```

## Parameters

| Parameter | Type   | Description |
| --------- | ------ | ----------- |
| key       | string |             |

Returns:

boolean

## Example

```js

```
